{"title":"西财摄记 ｜ 拥抱最后的夏天","uid":"86deda4bc8055be095eccdd3214944c8","slug":"推文8","date":"2021-09-26T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-03-03T15:38:50.856Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/推文8.json","keywords":null,"cover":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231455106.png","content":"<p>“我仍记得，</p>\n<p>夏日橘子汽水的心动。”</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231352889.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231352889\"></p>\n<p>你在夏天会喝汽水吗？</p>\n<p>拉开易拉罐的拉环</p>\n<p>气泡混合着清新的甜味喷薄而出</p>\n<p>就像一声忍俊不禁的轻笑</p>\n<p>裹挟着夏日的喜悦</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231402581.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231402581\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231406248.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231406248\"></p>\n<p>一瓶橘子味的汽水</p>\n<p>足以将我拉回整个灿烂的夏天</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231415719.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231415719\"></p>\n<p>九月中旬 风歇雨停</p>\n<p>似乎能听见黄桷兰滑下枝头</p>\n<p>坠入夏末傍晚</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231424226.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231424226\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231428376.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231428376\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231432796.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231432796\"></p>\n<p>在这个夏末秋初</p>\n<p>遇见成都难能可见的阳光</p>\n<p>火火是个特别喜欢拍照的女孩子</p>\n<p>也是我们SWUFE了吗模特部的一员</p>\n<p>在大草坪拍一组胶片感写真</p>\n<p>不失为拥抱成都最后夏天的仪式感</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231449863.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231449863\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231455106.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231455106\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231459575.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231459575\"></p>\n<p>夏日是一场远道而来的浪漫</p>\n<p>我希望所有的日落</p>\n<p>都不会再逃跑</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231512104.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231512104\"></p>\n<p>“火火你看，你的发丝会发光噢”</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231520308.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231520308\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231527272.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231527272\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231532461.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231532461\"></p>\n<p>走出操场时</p>\n<p>不知倦的螗蜩仍在热烈地歌颂着夏天</p>\n<p>就让歌声追着我</p>\n<p>但我眼前只有九月</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231541946.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231541946\"></p>\n<p>阳光渐渐褪去</p>\n<p>夏日迎来末尾</p>\n<p>而十月</p>\n<p>将随之怒放</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303231552435.png\" alt=\"image-20220303231552435\"></p>\n<p>再次见面，就是天高云淡的秋天啦！</p>\n<details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>感谢</summary>\n<p>摄|zz同学 </p>\n<p>出镜|火火</p>\n<p>文|李宜霏 罗雯曦</p>\n\n</details>\n","text":"“我仍记得， 夏日橘子汽水的心动。” 你在夏天会喝汽水吗？ 拉开易拉罐的拉环 气泡混合着清新的甜味喷薄而出 就像一声忍俊不禁的轻笑 裹挟着夏日的喜悦 一瓶橘子味的汽水 足以将我拉回整个灿烂的夏天 九月中旬 风歇雨停 似乎能听见黄桷兰滑下枝头 坠入夏末傍晚 在这个夏末秋初 遇见成都...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":382,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"西财摄记","slug":"西财摄记","count":7,"path":"api/categories/西财摄记.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"夏","slug":"夏","count":6,"path":"api/tags/夏.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"Swufe了吗","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://gitee.com/deelsilcon/pics/raw/master/uPic/logo.jpg","link":"/","description":"分享生活，记录美好","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"weichat":{"icon":"/img/wechat.png","link":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303234741533.png"},"mail"